show.description: A young woman named Bridget meets a mysterious man who claims to be Santa Claus. Bridget is struggling with her financial situation and the expectations of her family, while "Mr. Santa" offers her a glimpse into a different, more magical reality. The film explores themes of love, fate, and finding happiness even amid life's challenges.
